  <h3>Live dashboard (FastAPI + WebSocket)</h3>
  <p>
    A FastAPI server streams anomaly alerts and agent reports to a WebSocket-connected frontend in real time. The dashboard shows the live event stream, flagged anomalies highlighted in context, and the full agent report rendered as it's generated — token by token via streaming inference on Groq.
  </p>

